                    <div class="container">
                        <i class="ri-headphone-line icon"></i>
                        <h3>Feel free to book a call and get all the answers you need.</h3>
                        <a href="/book" class="btn">Book a call</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Second column -->
                <div class="heart-column-2 grid grid-rows-3 gap-4">
                    <div class="border-b py-6">
                        <button
                            class="flex justify-between items-center w-full text-left text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-600"
                            onclick="toggleSection('section10')">
                            Financial Services
                            <span class="text-gray-500">+</span>
                        </button>
                        <div id="section10" class="mt-2 hidden">
                            <p class="text-gray-700">Emiri FinTech has played a pivotal role in numerous high-profile
                                financial disputes over the past decade. Our clients, including retail, commercial, and
                                wholesale banks, insurers, payment companies, fintech firms, and wealth and asset
                                managers, depend on us for top-tier research, expert testimony, and comprehensive
                                support in litigation and regulatory matters. Our team comprises professionals with
                                backgrounds in finance and accounting, collaborating with leading academics and former
                                members of regulatory bodies such as the SEC, CFTC, DOJ, and European Commission. We
                                excel in consumer finance, particularly in areas like fair lending, non-discrimination,
                                and regulatory compliance. Emiri FinTech also assists financial institutions in
                                navigating the evolving regulatory and competitive landscape, optimizing strategies for
                                capital allocation, market models, and organizational structures to drive value
                                creation.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="border-b py-6">
                        <button
                            class="flex justify-between items-center w-full text-left text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-600"
                            onclick="toggleSection('section11')">
                            Investigations & Compliance
                            <span class="text-gray-500">+</span>
                        </button>
                        <div id="section11" class="mt-2 hidden">
                            <p class="text-gray-700">Clients and their legal teams frequently rely on Emiri FinTech's
                                investigations and compliance experts to address a wide array of allegations, including
                                fraud, corruption, money laundering, theft of trade secrets, accounting and financial
                                reporting issues, cybercrime, False Claims Act violations, and employee misconduct. We
                                also provide comprehensive investigative due diligence, business intelligence, and
                                evaluate and develop effective compliance programs.

                                Emiri FinTech deploys cross-functional teams to conduct large-scale, complex
                                investigations and monitorships that require a blend of data analytics, forensic
                                accounting, investigative, cyber, e-discovery, and subject matter expertise. Our
                                professionals include former prosecutors and government agents, white-collar
                                investigators, data analytics and cyber specialists, forensic accountants, damages
                                experts, and risk management professionals.

                                We offer a multidisciplinary and strategic approach to investigations, delivering
                                actionable intelligence and expert advice to law firms, financial institutions,
                                government regulators, multinational corporations, and other organizations worldwide.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="border-b py-6">
                        <button
                            class="flex justify-between items-center w-full text-left text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-600"
                            onclick="toggleSection('section12')">
                            Financial Litigation & Regulation
                            <span class="text-gray-500">+</span>
                        </button>
                        <div id="section12" class="mt-2 hidden">
                            <p class="text-gray-700">Emiri FinTech has extensive experience in handling high-profile,
                                complex financial litigation and regulatory issues. We assist organizations across
                                various industries through all stages of financial litigation, with specialized
                                expertise in securities, commodities, derivatives, mortgage, finance, and consumer
                                litigation. Emiri FinTech also offers a wide range of services related to financial
                                regulation. We help financial institutions manage compliance risks, develop and validate
                                financial models, and navigate changes in the competitive landscape of financial
                                markets. Additionally, we provide guidance through arbitration and dispute resolution
                                processes.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
